data.description: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY 2/24/24 11AM-2PM.Welcome to a paradigm of sophisticated living in this single-story sanctuary, a 4-bedroom, 2-bath haven spanning 2,383 sq ft. This energy-efficient masterpiece, artfully designed with an open floor plan and soaring ceilings, seamlessly blending luxury and practicality.    Situated on a serene cul-de-sac, this residence embraces the tranquility of its greenbelt surroundings, adorned with majestic oaks that grace the landscape, visible from the comfort of your covered back porch. Step into a realm of culinary delight in the gourmet kitchen, equipped with stainless steel appliances, a gas cooktop, and built-in oven & microwave, providing a harmonious balance of style and functionality.    The master bedroom stands as a testament to opulence, boasting two walk-in closets and an attached bonus room, perfect for a private office, nursery, or home gym, tailored to your lifestyle. The master bath is a retreat in itself, featuring a spacious shower, double sinks, and a makeup area, elevating your daily routine to a spa-like experience.    In the heart of a cul-de-sac, embraced by nature's beauty, and enriched with modern amenities, this home beckons you to indulge in a life of comfort and sophistication. Discover the epitome of upscale living in this meticulously curated, energy-efficient abode including a SweetWater water softener, laundry and air purifier system.
